FBIS3-23026 "jptot008__l94127" JPRS-TOT-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 1 March 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY PKK Bombs Istanbul Train Station, Kills Over 40 Cadets Bomb in Garbage Bin TA1202082394 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 0800 GMT 12 Feb 94 TA1202082394 Ankara TRT Television Network Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Announcer-read report; See SELECTED VIDEO REPORTS section for video footage of incident] [Text] According to initial reports, one person was killed and 10 were injured when a bomb placed in a garbage bin at the Tuzla train station in Istanbul exploded. According to a TRT correspondent, a bomb placed in a garbage bin at the Tuzla train station exploded around 0915. One person was killed and 10 were injured in the explosion. Most of the victims consist of the non-commissioned officers at the Tuzla Infantry School. Investigation into the incident is underway.
